Package: maschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Massachusetts School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", email = "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Al Martin <almartin@example.com>
Maintainer: Al Martin <almartin@example.com>
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Massachusetts Department
    of Elementary and Secondary Education (DESE). Provides functions for fetching
    enrollment data via the DESE Socrata API (educationtocareer.data.mass.gov) and
    transforming it into tidy format for analysis. Supports data from 1994-2025.
